msgstr "Lagringslägesgenomsökning kördes nyligen. Försök igen om %d sekunder."

#: includes/class-block-inventory.php:607
msgid "(deleted pattern)"
msgstr "(borttaget mönster)"

#: includes/class-block-mutator.php:102
msgid "Path must be an array of non-negative integers."
msgstr "Sökvägen måste vara en array av icke-negativa heltal."

#: includes/class-block-mutator.php:107
msgid "Path cannot be empty."
msgstr "Sökvägen får inte vara tom."

#: includes/class-block-mutator.php:122
#. translators: 1: segment index in path, 2: requested index, 3: valid range, 4: partial path
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Path segment %1$d (index %2$d) is out of bounds. Valid indices at this "
"level: %3$s. Partial path up to failure: [%4$s]. Run GET "
"/posts/{id}/blocks?outline=true to see the page structure."
msgstr ""
"Sökvägssegment %1$d (index %2$d) ligger utanför gränserna. Giltiga index på "
"denna nivå: %3$s. Delvis sökväg fram till fel: [%4$s]. Kör GET "
"/posts/{id}/blocks?outline=true för att se sidstrukturen."

#: includes/class-block-mutator.php:143
#. translators: 1: block name, 2: partial path
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Block \"%1$s\" at [%2$s] has no inner blocks. Cannot traverse into it. Use "
"update-attrs/update-html on this block directly, or wrap-in-group to add "
"children."
msgstr ""
"Block \"%1$s\" på [%2$s] har inga inre block. Kan inte traverseras. Använd "
"update-attrs/update-html direkt på detta block, eller wrap-in-group för att "
"lägga till barn."

#: includes/class-block-mutator.php:158
msgid "Path traversal encountered invalid block structure."
msgstr "Sökvägstrafik stötte på ogiltig blockstruktur."

#: includes/class-block-mutator.php:170
#. translators: 1: requested target index, 2: valid range
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Target block at index %1$d not found. Valid indices at this level: %2$s. "
"Run GET /posts/{id}/blocks?outline=true to see the page structure."
msgstr ""
"Målblock på index %1$d hittades inte. Giltiga index på denna nivå: %2$s. "
"Kör GET /posts/{id}/blocks?outline=true för att se sidstrukturen."

#: includes/class-block-mutator.php:189
